headline: Pillsbury(TM) Brings its Most Popular Halloween Recipe to Life – Launching a Crescent Mummy Dog Costume for Pets
summary: MINNEAPOLIS, September 10, 2025--Every October, one recipe rules Halloween on Pillsbury.com: Crescent Mummy Dogs. This year, Pillsbury is taking the beloved recipe beyond the kitchen with the launch of a limited-edition Crescent Mummy Dog costume for wiener dogs. The brand is also teaming up with DoorDash to make enjoying the recipe at home easier (and more fun) than ever.

headline: Could Buying High-Yield General Mills Today Set You Up for Life?
summary: General Mills' dividend yield is up to 4.8%; the dividend has trended higher for decades, but it hasn't been increased every single year.
